imdb.plot outline: Toronto Under Lenses T.U.L., this is our Web Series Version. It's an anticipation of the TV Show in development. It's an informal reality show, lightly documenting, about real life, of facts and 'dis-facts' that we, very normal citizens, encounter every day, dealing with media, 'truth', opinions, assertions, theories, anti-theories, critics, beliefs, and also facts, situations, small and big, in our city of Toronto, but projected worldwide; all depicted in our unique way.
